commitResults.messageTitle: Add horizontal lines seperating greet and exit messages

commitResults.messageBody:
Add indentation for output (including Level-0)
Implement echo of user input
Add exit when user input is "bye"

Add Task class used to create new Tasks that are stored in taskList which is an array of Tasks.
Add list command which loops through taskList to output tasks.

Add the ability to mark tasks as done
Add boolean isDone to Task class to indicate whether task is done or not
Add toString method to Task class
Rename Task[] from taskList to tasksList (coding standard)

Add ToDo, Deadline and Event Classes that inherit from Task class
Refactor code in Duke class:
-Remove magic literals by adding constants
-Extract methods to print welcome message, exit message, new task, completion of task, and list of tasks
-Extract method (inputLoop) to replace while loop in main method
